data.description: Welcome home!  Come check out this beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Arbors!  This spacious unit has over 1000 sq feet and also has a lanai space upstairs!  No need for assigned outdoor parking spots, Park in your two car garage!  Recent updates to the house are Flooring, Paint, and split AC system!  Stay cool in your home with your nice new split AC system!  Arbors is a gated community, featuring a pool, and BBQ Area when you enter.  Easy commute to stores, parks, restaurants and more!  Easy access to H1.  $2000 closing credit offered to buyers with full price offer!
